{"tid":882424,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【爆汗好機會】蔡思貝一邊做瑜伽一邊賣樓盤","createTime":"2018-10-30T06:20:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-31T04:35:56.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"feeae8eaa5ed19adc498e55396401067359db74b","tid":882424,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T06:20:58.000Z","msg":"蔡思貝最近正為劇集《機場特警》開工，劇中講佢要喺學堂受訓，極考驗體能。唔好以為思貝咁瘦就一定潺，平時佢有做開運動，體能絕對唔差，仲頂得住0架：「因為我哋做呢行，開工時間好唔穏定，跑步同做瑜珈都可以自己做，唔駛約朋友，又唔使教練都做到。」<br />\n做運動強身健體，做到可以賣樓盤&hellip;&hellip;廣告，佢獲邀場去北角一個樓盤做宣傳，示範瑜珈。佢話︰「我平時跑步同行山都可以喺屋企附近，我本身都住北角，有時會去近屋企寶馬山、賽西湖行吓，出一身汗可以飛返屋企沖涼，根住先去做嘢！」咁有冇諗過喺同區買個新單位住？「梗係想啦，所以要努力工作囉，今日都有睇過樓盤嘅設計，最吸引我個室外活動空間，外型好似一個水晶球大空館咁，好靚好得意。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181030/large/1540877547_ae14.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181030%2Flarge%2F1540877547_ae14.jpg&h=e75bcfd7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"87d16dec68d28b2f0d105924b00664962bf11fe7","tid":882424,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T06:52:17.000Z","msg":"國力<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e48bc73aeb084baf32c20f6a65bf79713bd0f1f","tid":882424,"uid":122703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T08:50:13.000Z","msg":"瑜珈學碩士"},{"pid":"82164dcd459f6ccf17f1c1990cec82f745ace1fe","tid":882424,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87d16dec68d28b2f0d105924b00664962bf11fe7","tid":882424,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T06:52:17.000Z","msg":"國力<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T04:35:56.000Z","msg":"佢了解完未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}